description: Welcome to this fantastic opportunity to rent in South Boston with TWO GARAGE PARKING SPOTS. This residence at 366 West Second Street offers a spacious 2 Bedrooms and 1.5 Bathrooms in the heart of Southie. Come see this wonderfully spaced open concept kit/liv/din with a gas FP. Kitchen features granite counters & SS appliances, with high top breakfast bar. Stay cool with Central AC. The Master Bedroom has a walk-in closet and Master Bath. Additional features include HW floors, surround sound, in unit W/D, basement storage unit, and ample closet space. Enjoy amazing views of Boston from your new private roof deck. Steps away from local restaurants, shops, grocery store, beach, and public transportation. FLEX move in date.
